### POST /api/v1/oversikt
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/oversikt
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("azure")}}

{
    "identitetsnummer": "{{identitetsnummer}}",
    "paging": {
        "page": 1,
        "page_size": 10,
        "sort_order": "DESC"
    }
}